{"word":"G1973 - ἐπιπόθητος - epipóthētos - ep-ee-poth'-ay-tos - Longed for","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιπόθητος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epipóthētos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-poth'-ay-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Longed for</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"வாஞ்சையான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"longed for"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and a derivative of the latter part of <a href=\"#/G1971 - ἐπιποθέω - epipothéō - ep-ee-poth-eh'-o/1971\">G1971</a>; <i>yearned upon</i>, that is, <i>greatly loved:</i> - longed for.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}